VALUES ('d2c36c95-b0ed-422c-a8f0-eb0bc3f9998b', 'Which choice completes the text with the most logical transition?', 'A startup claimed its algorithm could screen job applicants more fairly than human recruiters by ignoring names and photographs. Auditors discovered that the system had learned to favor candidates whose hobbies and zip codes correlated with the firm''s mostly affluent past hires. ______, an approach designed to erase bias had merely relocated it to variables that looked neutral on their surface.', NULL, '[{"id":"A","text":"In fact,","is_correct":true,"explanation":"In fact intensifies and confirms the troubling reality the audit exposed, sharpening that the bias was relocated, not removed."},{"id":"B","text":"Nevertheless,","is_correct":false,"explanation":"Nevertheless signals contrast, but the sentence reinforces the audit''s finding rather than opposing it."},{"id":"C","text":"By contrast,","is_correct":false,"explanation":"By contrast sets two things in opposition, but the sentence restates and strengthens the same point."},{"id":"D","text":"Hopefully,","is_correct":false,"explanation":"Hopefully expresses a wish, which does not fit a sentence stating an established negative finding."}]'::jsonb, 'A', 'Step 1 — Find the audit finding
The system favored candidates whose {{yellow:hobbies and zip codes correlated with the firm''s mostly affluent past hires}}.
Step 2 — Why In fact
The final sentence drives home the stronger truth that bias was relocated, not erased, so the intensifying ''In fact'' fits.
Distractor analysis:
- B: Nevertheless implies contrast, but the sentence agrees with and amplifies the finding.
- C: By contrast needs opposition, which is absent.
- D: Hopefully voices a wish, inappropriate for a stated negative result.', 'Does the last sentence push back on the audit or drive its point home more forcefully?', 'Expression of Ideas', 'Transitions', 'reading_writing', 'expression', 'TRA', NULL, 'hard', false, 'SAT', 'multiple_choice', true, true, 'scholaris_ai', '{"generator":"scholaris_ai_v1","model":"gemma-4-26b-a4b-it","original":true,"explanation_v2":true}'::jsonb, now(), now())
